Subject: Re: [VB] Camper headliner

Try a product called Thermo Ply, its used by builders between the brick
and the house during construction. Its flexible $5.00 for a 4x8 sheet and
about 1/8" in thickness. You may have to call around to find it but its
cheap and easy to work with.

Stan Wilder

